jobs_results.description:
We are looking for a Mobile Developer for our Media IT & Telco area.

You will be in charge of the design, development and maintenance of mobile, native and cross-platform applications. You will work closely with the client and other mobile developers to coordinate and manage project activities.

Activities:
• Managing the development of new mobile app features developed in React Native on all platforms (Android, iOS, Huawei, Galaxy...).

Key requirements:
• Hands-on experience with React Native;
• Knowledge of Swift/Kotlin;
• Knowledge of Typescript, ES6, GIT, Redux, Zustand.

Qualifications:
• Bachelor's degree in Computer Science or Computer Engineering;
• At least 3 years of experience in the role;
• Excellent knowledge of the English language.

Location: Naples and Milan
